Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:47.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ulquiorra, coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:55.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come...\NUlquiorra... Yammy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just finishing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:06.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How much of the Hogyoku\Nhas awakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone about halfway.\NThings are going as planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For Soul Society, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:14.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be able to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you held the Hogyoku\Nin your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:26.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke Urahara sealed it away\Nas soon as he developed it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:29.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and he never unsealed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even he probably\Ndoesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:36.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After being unsealed and\Nin a sleeping state,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when the Hogyoku temporarily fuses\Nwith someone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with the Spiritual Pressure\Nof a captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:50.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For an instant, it displays the same power\Nas if it were completely awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:03.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me your name,\Nmy new comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderweiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:14.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderweiss...Margera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember\Nthe instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I mentioned about\Na month ago, Ulquiorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:29.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it into action.\NI'll give you the final say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:32.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take with you\Nwhomever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:47.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish to\Ngo as well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grimmjow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:03:59.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:11.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're already dead..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that\Nthis line is deep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the middle of battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:22.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,telling people who haven't realized\Nthat they've died that they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:30.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't you realize it?\NYou're alive, but you're already dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That line's not something\Nin line with Schiele.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:37.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, could you stop reading\Nthe manga I buy before I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and telling me\Nwhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:47.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do you think\Nyou died just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:48.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:52.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that Soul Reapers\Nhave the godly ability
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep on dying,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they don't, baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner!\NGather round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:10.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who gets here last\Nhas to wash the dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:19.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Hiyori, is Ichigo making progress\Nin maintaining his Hollow transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell by looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's just a little\Nover ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:29.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worthless!\NThat baldy's not worth talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:36.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he doesn't have any talent.\NGive up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, erotica woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not participating\Nin my training,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so you've no right\Nto say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am participating, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:49.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget that I secretly\Nlent you some erotica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't lend me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make jokes like that!\NThey sound true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:56.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be bashful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrow some once every two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:06.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I read some twice a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:11.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I've never been like you,\Nyou perverted woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:16.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not perverted!\NI'm just very curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:20.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,People call that perversity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:24.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But you're\Ninterested, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:25.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Wait up!\N- A little over ten seconds in a month.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:33.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought,\Nwe need time to do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:40.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Hogyoku completely awakens\N at the end of December...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have two months\Nuntil then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've got to go\Na little faster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:01.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hisagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:08.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was watching them while\NI was taking a bit of a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:16.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're training in preparation\Nfor the showdown in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kuchiki and\NOrihime Inoue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I met her in\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 33: Sokatsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're\Nenjoying their training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:53.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Captain Ukitake,\NI have a personal request.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:57.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A personal request?\NWhat is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to open the training ground\Nbehind the barracks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The training ground?\NWhy now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:10.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, sir! A friend and I\Nwant to train{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in preparation for\Nthe showdown in winter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:17.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}C-Captain Ukitake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've brought you Orihime Inoue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:26.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you saying,\Nyou stinky-armpit monkey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the one who brought her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:30.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't lie, you snotty woman!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:34.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, Captain Ukitake...\NWould you like more tea?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:34.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not fair!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:37.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You promised\Nthat we'd decide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who gets to pour him tea\Nwith Rock-Paper-Scissors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person who makes\Nthe first move wins!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Sorry...\Nfor being selfish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I came here so suddenly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inoue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no need to be modest!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:55.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our final goal is\Nour showdown with Aizen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as we have\Nsomebody with powers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Soul Reaper or a human,\Nit doesn't matter which!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:05.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look! I'd even want Chappy's help\Nin this situation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:07.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, pyon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:11.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kuchiki, you don't need to\Nadjust things to my level.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:15.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway... Let's train!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's fine as long\Nas you understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's do our best, Inoue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:23.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When she asked me\Nto open up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:33.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the training ground with\Nsuch a desperate look,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering\Nwhat was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad that\Nshe's made a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:46.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if...she's a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:53.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:59.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends are good even if\Nthey lead different lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:04.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides,\Nshe's not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:08.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When she comes to Soul Society,\Nshe might become a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:17.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 33: Sokatsui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Santenkesshun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:26.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:28.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotenzanshun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back!\NYour hesitation is your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hado 4:\NByakurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Santenkesshun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:57.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\Nwhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:00.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something\Nyou have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!\NHere, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,SEIREITEI NEWS\N\N\NHere's this month's\N	Seireitei News.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mail-order\Ncatalog inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why are\Nyou doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:12.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm overwhelmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 10's captain and\Nlieutenant are both
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:17.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:22.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 11's captain\Nis sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't know where\Ntheir lieutenant is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:30.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,BIO LAB SIX\NDO NOT ENTER\N	I'LL KILL YOU IF YOU COME IN\N\N	Squad 12's captain and lieutenant\N	haven't come out from the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:36.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly never knew that\Na captain's duties were so hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Tosen never asked\Nhis subordinate to do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,\NI'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:50.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...\Nrelax here for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:54.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:58.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind watching\Ntwo girls train, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Invite me again when I have\Na little more free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:10.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Four months...\NA short time to heal the soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's an even shorter time\Nto get stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:26.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can only hope this temporary peace\Nlasts as long as possible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:36.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Crap! Crap! Crap! Crap!\NYou bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Take this!\NTake this! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Break! Break!\NBreak! Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:41.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:43.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw... This is so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you be quiet\Nfor a moment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:51.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Fujikujaku is\Nso annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so overbearing\Nand arrogant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and thinks that he's the most\Nbeautiful person in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:03.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he'll ever\Nmanifest himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:03.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it even if\Nhe asks me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:10.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NHe's exactly like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:17.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Haineko is selfish,\Ntemperamental, lazy and stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really what you would\Ncall not getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:25.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...\NYou're exactly alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku, you're the type of\Nperson who would look
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:31.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,at a picture of yourself and\Nsay "this isn't how I look"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:35.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, Yumichika?\NSay that once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yumichika, so I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you shut up!\NConcentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you back\Nto Soul Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:44.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even calm down and\Ncommunicate with your swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:01.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those clouds\Nare moving fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something,\NMadarame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No...It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrancars?! No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this is\Na little too early?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:38.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is indeed too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have any time\Nto think about why they've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to\Na nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:50.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some pretty strong\NSpiritual Pressures wandering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:56.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NThey're Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably the reinforcements\N from Soul Society
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:02.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that Mr. Number Six\Nwas talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:09.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sorry.\NYou're "formerly" Mr. Number Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:15.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy I want to kill\Nisn't in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:17.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:19.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Wait, Grimmjow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:21.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just an Espada dropout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:29.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:38.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy I want to kill\Nisn't down there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:42.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to fight the guy\Nwho cut off your arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:47.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who beat you up,\Nor the one who reflected your Cero?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:50.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let's go, newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going\Nto just stand there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Another strange one's joined us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A signal!\NWe've got an Arrancar signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Gentei Kaijo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:17.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already\Nreceived permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What color is the signal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crimson signal!\NIt's an Espada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:34.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Squad 10 Captain,\NToshiro Hitsugaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence...\NI'm also a ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:42.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Arrancar Diez, Yammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Diez?! Number ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,An Espada, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:49.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to know\Na lot about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you fought\Nsomeone pretty talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an Espada, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...\NMy name is Luppi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My rank is Seis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:23.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I\Nshould kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:27.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you,\Nwe still can't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:35.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends from Soul Society\Nare stationed here for things like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:41.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been training\Nfor times like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What good is it\Nif I don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:50.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:57.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:09.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I got word of it\Njust now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:17.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kido Corps should be\Nopening the gate right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the Senkaimon\N in front of the barracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:21.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:24.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:27.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:31.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have\Na Hell Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:33.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you go with me\Nthrough the Senkaimon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be sent to the Dangai,\NPrecipice World.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've given out orders to stabilize\Nthe walls of the Dangai, Precipice World,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you can\Npass through it safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take about a half hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can go to\Nthe World of the Living then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in a rush,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's important not to be\Nhasty at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:55.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going ahead.\NI'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:03.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't be!\NThe Espada?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:13.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there are several of them...\NIt's too early!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wasn't the Hogyoku supposed\Nto awaken later on?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What in the world\Nis going on?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:37.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I've been looking\Nfor you, Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:48.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,how much I've changed\Nin the past month!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:52.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:10.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Bankai?\NSo what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:17.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bankai didn't do\Nanything against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:20.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:26.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My attacks gave you that scar\Nwhen I used my Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:34.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you\None thing, Grimmjow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened\Nto your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:41.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I discarded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:47.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unnecessary to kill you\Nwith two arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:49.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:56.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't need to\Nhold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:00.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to die, then don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, the amount\Nof time I can maintain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:10.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a Hollow transformation\N is eleven seconds flat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:13.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to settle this\Nwithin that time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:17.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA'S SHOP\NI told you that you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've overused your powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:24.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go. You rest here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:30.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right,\Nit's as Abarai says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:35.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Abarai is\Nexhausted as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:40.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:47.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.26,0:23:21.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure\NI don't have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:22.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:26.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of that, organize\Nthe merchandise that I purchased.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:28.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean all those things\N you bought, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurodo, Noba, help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:31.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:32.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:33.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:35.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:36.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:41.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,SEIREITEI NEWS\NEDITORIAL DEPARTMENT\N\N	Aw... Busy, busy, busy,\N	busy, busy, busy, busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Rangiku's article finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:43.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:45.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:48.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought Squad 8's article.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:53.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'm glad that Squad 8\Nalways sticks to deadlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:54.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:57.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an Arrancar signal\Nin the World of the Living!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:58.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an Espada!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:02.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I've got to go to cover\Nthe event for a special feature!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:05.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what\Nyou're supposed to do...